  <scopecontent id="aspace_337afda8a6e8d74714c9d3de3008fd75">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Examples of various historical writing systems and scripts, including hieroglyphics on fragments of papyrus, reed sticks with proto-Arabian inscriptions, cuneiform tablets, a bowl inscribed in Etruscan, Aramaic incantation bowls, a bronze piece with a runic inscription, Arabic on cloth fragments, decorated 13th-century Bible leaves, and other writings through the 18th century.</p>  </scopecontent>
